data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: There is a group of men in this picture. One man wears a blue shirt and he is holding a microphone and helping a presenter with his presentation. the presenter wears a pair of black glasses, and he is holding a piece of paper in his hand. Another man, who is standing next to a red wall, is looking at the presenter’s paper and he has smiles on his face. In the background, there is a poster on the red wall. Also, there is a man standing behind. He wears a dark green sweater and he has short hair.
